1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

CVSS v4 8.4
ATTENTION: Low Attack Complexity
Vendor: Siemens
Equipment: Siemens Engineering Platforms
Vulnerability: Deserialization of Untrusted Data

2. RISK EVALUATION
